{"tid":209382,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"歸英賴綺雯選舉呈請成功申請法援","createTime":"2017-04-20T07:23:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-22T00:26:04.000Z","uid":92301,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d259064efb5d54ec9b4bc286cca6d11ac192c488","tid":209382,"uid":92301,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T07:23:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/k8htuves\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fk8htuves&h=78e58b8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nAlice Lai 賴綺雯就選舉呈請嘅法援申請，上訴成功。 <br />\n<br />\n賴綺雯就2016年立法會選舉提出選舉呈請，並申請法援，近日法援申請上訴成功，取得法援。捍衞香港人嘅選舉權同言論自由至為重要。賴綺雯亦會繼續要求英國履行對香港嘅承諾同埋《中英聯合聲明》嘅責任，及考慮將香港歸還英國，成為英國海外領土。<br />\n<br />\nAlice Lai was success to appeal the decision to refuse her legal aid for lodging the election petition against the 2016 Legislative Council Election. She was granted an application for legal aid funding. It is vital important to uphold the electoral rights and freedom of speech of all Hongkongers. Alice Lai will also be continuing to urge Her Majesty&rsquo;s Government to fulfil its promises on Hong Kong, as stated in the Sino-British Joint Declaration, at the same time be open to the option of Hong Kong reuniting with the UK as a British Overseas Territory.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/ConservativePartyHK/photos/a.701989989902501.1073741828.641167375984763/1042870285814468/?type=3&amp;source=54\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2FConservativePartyHK%2Fphotos%2Fa.701989989902501.1073741828.641167375984763%2F1042870285814468%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26source%3D54&d=C%2Fe7%2FQel5OtnIpuNpUi2IE%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=6ff4e673\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/ConservativePartyHK/photos/a.701989989902501.1073741828.641167375984763/1042870285814468/?type=3&amp;source=54</a>"},{"pid":"45f9a94e2bf1441c190966050562ff1d71e8ac85","tid":209382,"uid":92301,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-2