=\"hkgmoji\" />係就好"},{"pid":"da1d9ccf4f1db97a48812b5e161e96c153b02df1","tid":209382,"uid":78016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T12:49:22.000Z","msg":"英女皇要拆呢個難題好簡單<br />\n開出歸英條件:<br />\n50% 以上腥港人 IELTS 7分或以上<br />\n咁樣歸英撚就會死心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n實際10%都唔知有無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f65fdcc5f0b045fd8978cda2eba9b12c2fc1de6c","tid":209382,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T13:05:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>歸英無可能，港獨又有可能？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />兩邊都冇咩可能，咁點解連登仔恥笑歸英，但唔恥笑港獨既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n先有港獨再歸英<br />\n香港脫離中國獨立唔到就唔會歸英<br />\n港獨成功亦唔一定要歸英<br />\n所以論冇可能嘅<br />\n歸英一定比港獨嘅可能性更低</blockquote><br />\n佢唔係話歸英然後獨立咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我反而覺得歸英可能性比獨立大<br />\n<br />\n因為只要證明到中英聯合聲明失效就得(有人做緊)<br />\n<br />\n但係我都係想香港獨立多啲</blockquote><br />\n(有人做緊) 有冇機會幫到手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe8d95daeca521853fe92bc13ce9c0b6bb793eb6","tid":209382,"uid":16731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T13:14:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"63efe477935740e93aaddbb3d1145b7c3d8d6ba0","tid":209382,"uid":16731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T13:14:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fcca0ff846422ab20d10b90553baa334681a49ad","tid":209382,"uid":42767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T13:17:27.000Z","msg":"想當年班歸英派響高登係大勢所趨, 一年左右就收曬皮<br />\nsarina-uk 之流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85fdac0094617929b34d86f3aa31b841f2b2df86","tid":2093